Does the new Battlestar Galactica series have more episodes than the old one?
column4: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>ASK WHERE {	<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlestar_Galactica_%281978_TV_series%29> dbo:numberOfEpisodes ?x .	<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlestar_Galactica_%282004_TV_series%29> dbo:numberOfEpisodes ?y .	FILTER (?y > ?x)}
